Join US state abbreviations to a data frame

key_state.Rd

Join US state abbreviations to a data frame

key_state(x)

Arguments

x

object with an unabbreviated state column

Examples

key_state(data.frame(state.name = datasets::state.name, stringsAsFactors = FALSE))
